race.comment: IMMORTAL SHIELD (3) was beaten a nose last time and is close to a win. This is easier and has placed 3/4 around this circuit. Low draw and will go close again. FUSSY AS (1) has a win and three minors from four runs this time in and looks a danger. Raced on speed and placed in tougher last time on the Parks track and should take catching again. PAPAL WARS (2) is an interesting runner, having first run fora  new yard. Former Queenslander with form over further and does boast good early speed. Has a light weight and can give a sight fresh on his new home track. MORLAIX (9) has placed two of three this time in, the latest heavily bet where she ran on hard to place. Drawn for a soft run here and will wind up strongly. URBANISE (7) was well off her best last time when she faced the breeze throughout and weakened out. Drawn ideally here and can do better.
